verbose_text: XREF_BIBR XREF_BIBR XREF_BIBR XREF_BIBR The aim of this study was to assess whether the TEG 6s system can be used to monitor and quantify concentrations of UFH and LMWH in blood, to evaluate the use of combination TEG 6s parameters, and to confirm whether these parameters can effectively classify blood samples at subtherapeutic, therapeutic, and supratherapeutic levels of heparin.
